---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About | MidNite Shadow Online"
  description="Learn more about MidNite Shadow, the creator behind the content and projects featured on this site."
>
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container prose">
      <p class="eyebrow">About</p>
      <h1>MidNite Shadow</h1>
      <p class="lede">
        MidNite Shadow is a online alias/handle used by a content creator and
        developer with a passion for gaming, storytelling, and community
        engagement.
      </p>
      <p>
        I'm Steve, a UK-based software engineer, long-time gamer, virtual
        tabletop enthusiast, and creator operating online under the name MidNite
        Shadow 7.
      </p>
      <p>
        By day I work professionally in software engineering and systems
        development. Outside of that, I spend most of my time building tools,
        worlds, automation systems, media projects, and community resources
        centred around gaming, sci-fi, and storytelling.
      </p>
      <p>
        Over the years that has evolved into a collection of projects ranging
        from web applications and Roll20 mods to podcast production, streaming
        assets, campaign settings, and community tools.
      </p>
      <p>
        This site is designed to sit separately from a professional portfolio.
        It is deliberately more personal, atmospheric and project-focused.
      </p>
      <p>
        If you want to find out more about me and my professional work, you can
        visit my <a
          href="https://SteveRoberts.me"
          title="Steve Roberts' personal website"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer">https://SteveRoberts.me</a
        > site.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
